Column, pillar, capital</h1><div class=\"thlex-section\">\n<h2 class=\"thlex-heading\">References:</h2>\n<h3 class=\"thlex-subheading\">\n          <strong>Column</strong>:</h3>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-sets\">\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Hebrew</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">דְּבִיר</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(dvir)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr3:16\">2CH 3:16</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Hebrew</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">זָוִית</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(zawith)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps144:12\">PSA 144:12</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Hebrew</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">מִסְעָד</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(mis‘ad)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs10:12\">1KI 10:12</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Hebrew</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">מָצוּק</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(matsuq)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam2:8\">1SA 2:8</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Hebrew</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">עַמּוּד</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(‘amud)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod13:21\">EXO 13:21</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod13:21\">EXO 13:21</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod13:22\">EXO 13:22</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod13:22\">EXO 13:22</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod14:19\">EXO 14:19</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod14:24\">EXO 14:24</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod26:32\">EXO 26:32</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod26:37\">EXO 26:37</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod27:10\">EXO 27:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod27:10\">EXO 27:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref